- Choose the bin with the largest remaining space.
- Choose the bin with the smallest remaining space.
- Choose the bin with the remaining space closest to the item size.
- Choose the bin with the least number of items.
- Choose the bin with the most similar size to the item.
- Choose the bin with the least remaining space after placing the item.
- Choose the bin with the highest priority based on some function of the item and bin sizes.

