### Solution Code

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item - np.mean(bins)) * np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) + np.log(bins) * np.sqrt(item)
```

