```python
def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item - bins) * (item * np.std(bins)) + np.log(np.pi * (item / bins)) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * np.cos(np.pi * (item / bins))
```

