2. Ratio of item to bin capacity.
3. Standard deviation of bins to penalize variability.
4. Number of items in the bin.
5. Utilization rate of the bin (item / bins[i]).
6. Similarity between item and bin size.
7. Bin's remaining capacity after adding the item.
8. Some combination of the above features, possibly weighted.

### Implementation Ideas:

